<abstract><t>This memo describes the RTCP Payload-Specific Feedback Message "Layer Refresh Request" (LRR), which can be used to request a state refresh of one or more substreams of a layered media stream.  It also defines its use with several RTP payloads for scalable media formats.</t></abstract>

